    "summary": "The user asks for confirmation on whether consuming a small amount of alcohol (red wine) alongside their prescribed diazepam would be safe or if \"the worst that happens\" is significant. The assistant repeatedly and correctly refuses to validate this behavior, warning of respiratory depression and unpredictable interactions, while directing the user to consult their doctor.",
